title: Quality Living. It Starts Here at Breckinridge Point!
posting_body: ['Breckinridge Point is the perfect place to find your new home in North Dallas!', 'We offer luxury one, two, and three-bedroom apartments in Richardson for rent.', 'Our location is close to US 75 and has several top schools nearby.', 'Breckinridge Point has several home options to best suit your lifestyle, from townhome-style apartments to units that have attached garages.', 'Schedule a tour to discover all of our apartment and home amenities and join our community!', '-Swimming Pool', '-Spacious Closets', '-Dog Park', '-Stainless Steel Appliances', '-Energy Efficient Appliances', '-Outdoor', 'Storage', '-Washer/Dryer Connections', '-BBQ/Picnic Area', '-Billiards Area w/ Poker Tables', '-Covered Parking Available', '-Online Rent Payment & Service Requests', '-Fitness Center', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and availability subject to change.', 'Equal housing opportunity.']
